        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Chop <strong>half </strong>of your<strong> Thai basil</strong> finely, including the stalks and keep the<strong> remaining Thai basil leaves </strong>whole</p><p>Crush your <strong>garlic </strong>open by squashing it with the side of a knife and remove the skins</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1723199530327-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
