            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>crushed garlic </strong>and <strong>chopped Thai basil</strong> to a <strong>pestle & mortar</strong> with 1 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp] </span><strong>sugar</strong> and grind to a paste</p><p>Add your <strong>Thai green curry paste </strong>with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil </strong>and stir it all together – this is your <strong>fragrant Thai green curry paste</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
