    {
      "instruction": "<p>Chop your <strong>creamed coconut</strong> roughly (if required!)</p><p>Once softened, add the <strong>fragrant Thai green curry paste</strong> with 2 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[3 tsp] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tsp] </span><strong>flour </strong>and cook for 1-2 min or until fragrant</p><p>Once fragrant, add your <strong>creamed coconut </strong>and<strong> lime leaf[ves] </strong>with 150ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[200ml] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[250ml]</span> <strong>boiled water </strong>and give everything a mix up until the coconut has dissolved</p>",
