    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve your <strong>fragrant Thai green curry mussels </strong>with the <strong>cooked rice </strong>to the side</p><p>Tip: For fancy presentation, press the rice into a small bowl and turn out</p><p>Garnish with the <strong>whole Thai basil leaves</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
